%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20is%20showing%20the%20West%20why%20cheap%20sensors%20could%20be%20key%20to%20defending%20the%20skies%20in%20future%20wars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20camouflage%20gear%20and%20a%20helmet%20sits%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20black%20vehicle%20under%20a%20dark%20sky%20with%20a%20beam%20of%20white%20light%20going%20into%20the%20sky%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a33feb00e60dfb3f373eebc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECheap%20sensors%20are%20allowing%20Ukraine%20to%20detect%20incoming%20drone%20threats%20and%20are%20inspiring%20the%20West.%3Cp%3EMaksym%20Kishka%2FSuspilne%20Ukraine%2FJSC%20%26quot%3BUA%3APBC%26quot%3B%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20is%20using%20cheap%20sensor%20networks%20to%20detect%20Russian%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWestern%20defense%20officials%20say%20the%20West%20needs%20to%20copy%20parts%20of%20that%20model.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDrones%20fly%20lower%20and%20slower%20than%20the%20threats%20many%20Western%20defenses%20were%20built%20for.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20showing%20the%20West%20why%20cheap%20sensors%20could%20be%20important%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-teaching-nato-air-forces-lessons-fighting-russia-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eair%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20future%20wars%2C%20defense%20officials%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20militaries%20have%20advanced%20sensors%20built%20to%20detect%20incoming%20missiles%20and%20fighter%20jets%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-ukraine-operation-shows-drone-lessons-western-militaries-need-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20exposed%20capability%C2%A0gaps%20requiring%20new%20kinds%20of%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESir%20John%20Stringer%2C%20NATO's%20Deputy%20Supreme%20Allied%20Commander%20Europe%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20defensive%20air%20defense%20purposes%2C%20we%20need%20to%20get%20back%20to%20investing%20in%20the%20range%20of%20sensors%20that%20we%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20those%20are%20most%20definitely%20novel%20for%20many%20Western%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20West%20needs%20%26quot%3Bthings%20like%20very%20cheap%20acoustic%20sensors%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20microphone-based%20systems%20that%20listen%20for%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Band%20we've%20seen%20the%20lay%20down%20in%20Ukraine%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20alongside%20the%20more%20advanced%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20full-scale%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvasion%20of%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20drones%20a%20daily%20battlefield%20threat%2C%20and%20Western%20militaries%20are%20studying%20how%20to%20fight%20and%20defend%20in%20that%20kind%20of%20threat%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Figures%20in%20camouflage%20in%20a%20brown%20field%20launch%20a%20grey%20drone%20in%20front%20of%20trees%20and%20under%20a%20grey%20sky%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a340665f4bed3c6152cb7da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrones%20move%20differently%20in%20the%20air%20than%20crewed%20aircraft%20and%20missiles%20do.%3Cp%3EYevhen%20Titov%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMaj.%20Modris%20Kairi%C5%A1s%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Latvia's%20Autonomous%20Systems%20Competence%20Center%2C%20a%20drone-warfare%20testing%20and%20training%20hub%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20West%20needs%20%26quot%3Bto%20rebuild%20our%20system%2C%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20additional%20sensors%20for%20detecting%20things%20at%20low%20altitude%20because%20these%20drones%20are%20flying%20very%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20air%20defense%20systems%20were%20primarily%20built%20around%20aircraft%20and%20missiles%20that%20fly%20higher%20and%20faster%2C%20so%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20these%20issues%20with%20detection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKairi%C5%A1s%20said%20that%20while%20quantity%20is%20key%2C%20so%20is%20variety%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20every%20sensor%20has%20strong%20and%20weak%20points.%26quot%3B%20That%20gives%20cheap%20sensors%20a%20role%20alongside%20higher-end%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Western%20militaries%20do%20not%20need%20to%20start%20from%20scratch.%20They%20already%20have%20much%20of%20the%20technology%20they%20might%20need.%20The%20bigger%20issue%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20buying%20and%20fielding%20equipment%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Bronk%2C%20a%20top%20airpower%20expert%20at%20the%20UK-based%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20think%20tank%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20air%20defense%20is%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20complicated%20and%20requires%20linking%20together%20lots%20and%20lots%20of%20different%20types%20of%20sensors%26quot%3B%20to%20cover%20different%20areas%2C%20altitudes%2C%20and%20threat%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20handle%20different%20threats%2C%20he%20said%2C%20an%20effective%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-threats-air-defense-challenges-force-hard-choices-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eair%20defense%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Brequires%20you%20to%20layer%20multiple%20types%20of%20air%20and%20missile%20defense%20systems%20around%20an%20object%20or%20area%20that%20you%20want%20to%20protect%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20this%20ranges%20from%20the%20expensive%2C%20high-end%20interceptors%20to%20the%20cheaper%20ones%20designed%20with%20drones%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20using%20cheap%20sensor%20networks%2C%20including%20acoustic%20sensors%20that%20listen%20for%20incoming%20drones%20and%20cost%20far%20less%20than%20military%20radars.%20They%20form%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20air%20defense%20system%20that%20includes%20expensive%2C%20high-end%20equipment%2C%20and%20they%20help%20Ukraine%20spot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-is-sending-swarms-of-cheap-drones-after-single-soldiers-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elow-cost%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20enough%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Western%20officials%20want%20to%20copy%20parts%20of%20the%20model.%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Sean%20Gainey%2C%20then%20the%20commander%20of%20US%20Army%20Space%20and%20Missile%20Defense%20Command%2C%20said%20in%202024%20that%20the%20US%20ought%20to%20integrate%20the%20kind%20of%20low-cost%20acoustic%20sensors%20that%20Ukraine%20has%20into%20its%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Tom%20Goffus%2C%20then%20NATO's%20assistant%20secretary%20general%20for%20operations%2C%20said%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3Bessentially%2C%20Ukraine%20is%20covering%20its%20entire%20nation%2C%201%2C000%20meters%20and%20below%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20acoustic%20sensors%20for%20less%20than%20%2454%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20crazy%20what%20they're%20doing%20with%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrius%20Kubilius%2C%20the%20European%20Union's%20defense%20commissioner%2C%20warned%20last%20year%20that%20the%20West%20does%20%26quot%3Bnot%20have%20the%20capability%26quot%3B%20to%20detect%20drones%2C%20or%20only%20has%20a%20limited%20one.%20%26quot%3BOur%20radars%20see%20aircraft%2C%20they%20see%20missiles%2C%20but%20they%20do%20not%20see%20very%20precisely%20drones%20that%20fly%20very%2C%20very%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20plans%20for%20a%20European%20drone%20wall%20%E2%80%94%20a%20proposed%20network%20of%20sensors%20and%20defenses%20against%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20should%20emulate%20Ukraine's%20capabilities%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bit%20has%20capabilities%20that%20we%20don't%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20thousands%20of%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaltic%20countries%2C%20NATO%20members%20that%20border%20Russia%2C%20have%20announced%20or%20moved%20toward%20buying%20acoustic%20sensor%20systems%2C%20citing%20lessons%20from%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20are%20different%20targets%20from%20jets%20and%20missiles%2C%20flying%20lower%2C%20slower%2C%20and%20with%20smaller%20profiles%20that%20are%20harder%20for%20some%20traditional%20radar%20systems%20to%20pick%20up.%20Some%20defense%20companies%2C%20however%2C%20are%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-militaries-used-to-missile-threat-can-struggle-drones-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20radar%20systems%20designed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20detect%20small%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20traditional%20air-defense%20systems%20were%20designed%20around%20larger%2C%20faster%2C%20higher-flying%20missiles%20and%20aircraft.%20Many%20Western%20systems%20can%20detect%20drones%2C%20but%20they%20weren't%20optimized%20for%20that%20fight.%20Another%20issue%20is%20that%20using%20them%20against%20cheap%20drones%20can%20be%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECost%20matters%20because%20aerial%20threats%20have%20multiplied.%20Cheaper%20sensors%20let%20militaries%20cover%20more%20airspace%2C%20and%20Ukraine%20has%20reinforced%20a%20broader%20lesson%3A%20modern%20war%20can%20burn%20through%20equipment%20quickly%2C%20so%20Western%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwests-approach-weaponry-wrong-vs-russia-ukraine-defense-industry-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eneed%20larger%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20cheaper%20systems%20alongside%20advanced%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20camouflage-coloured%20defense%20system%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck%20points%20into%20the%20sky%20with%20figures%20standing%20around%20it%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a340523f4bed3c6152cb7ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20West's%20advanced%20air%20defense%20systems%20can%20detect%20and%20stop%20drones%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20threat%20they%20were%20primarily%20designed%20for.%3Cp%3EDominika%20Zarzycka%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStringer%20said%20the%20West's%20air%20defense%20response%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20on%20the%20right%20part%20of%20what%20we%20call%20the%20cost%20curve%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20using%20defenses%20that%20are%20not%20wildly%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20threats%20they%20are%20meant%20to%20stop.%20He%20said%20that%20a%20clear%20example%20of%20doing%20it%20wrong%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmissiles-flying-across-middle-east-air-defense-price-tag-grows-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20multimillion-dollar%20interceptors%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20far%20cheaper%20drone%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20Iranian-designed%20Shahed%20one-way%20attack%20drones%2C%20versions%20of%20which%20Russia%20also%20makes%2C%20cost%20an%20estimated%20%2420%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%20each%2C%20while%20US-made%20Patriot%20Advanced%20Capability-3%20(PAC-3)%20interceptors%20are%20estimated%20to%20cost%20roughly%20%243.7%20million%20each.%20That%20math%20is%20%26quot%3Bunsustainable%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20long%20air%20war%2C%20Stringer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20new%20sensors%20reflects%20a%20harder%20reality%20from%20Ukraine%3A%20future%20wars%20may%20make%20the%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-superiority-only-possible-short-bursts-us-air-force-officer-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eair%20dominance%3C%2Fa%3E%20Western%20militaries%20achieved%20in%20some%20recent%20conflicts%20much%20harder%20to%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Stringer%20said%20militaries%20can't%20give%20up%20trying.%20%26quot%3BYou%20still%20need%20to%20secure%20air%20superiority.%20The%20ways%20of%20doing%20it%20may%20change%2C%20but%20it%20fundamentally%20provides%20a%20foundation%20on%20which%20the%20entire%20joint%20force%20operates.%20So%20if%20you're%20not%20able%20to%20secure%20the%20access%20and%20then%20the%20maneuver%20that%20you%20force%20needs%2C%20then%20you're%20failing.%26quot%3B%20New%20sensors%2C%20he%20said%2C%20could%20be%20part%20of%20how%20militaries%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-showing-west-cheap-sensors-key-future-air-war-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782130605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a33fef3f4bed3c6152cb749%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-showing-west-cheap-sensors-key-future-air-war-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20is%20using%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20cheap%20sensors%20to%20detect%20incoming%20drone%20threats.%20Western%20officials%20say%20the%20West%20should%20consider%20doing%20the%20same.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20paid%20%241%2C000%20for%202%20nights%20in%20a%20hotel%20room%20facing%20Niagara%20Falls.%20It%20was%20totally%20worth%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20table%2C%20sofa%2C%20and%20chair%20in%20a%20hotel%20room%20backed%20by%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows%20and%20a%20Juliette%20balcony%20facing%20Niagara%20Falls%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894b00dcfc04e97619aff44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20went%20to%20Niagara%20Falls%2C%20Ontario%2C%20and%20booked%20two%20nights%20at%20the%20Sheraton%20Fallsview%20Hotel.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20spent%20two%20nights%20at%20the%20Sheraton%20Fallsview%20Hotel%20on%20the%20Canadian%20side%20of%20Niagara%20Falls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUpgraded%20guest%20rooms%20with%20views%20of%20the%20falls%20come%20with%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20%24500%20a%20night%2C%20I%20had%20some%20of%20the%20best%20views%20of%20Niagara%20Falls%20of%20my%20entire%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20right%20from%20bed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20forget%20stepping%20into%20Canada.%20In%20August%202022%2C%20I%20walked%20over%20the%20Rainbow%20Bridge%20connecting%20New%20York%20and%20Ontario%2C%20stopping%20briefly%20in%20the%20middle%20to%20watch%20and%20listen%20to%20the%20roaring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fniagara-falls-canada-photos-show-expectation-vs-reality%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENiagara%20Falls%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20my%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2010%20minutes%20later%2C%20I%20was%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fniagara-falls-sheraton-fallsview-hotel-room-review-canada-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESheraton%20Fallsview%20Hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I'd%20see%20the%20epic%20force%20of%20nature%20flow%20from%20my%20bedroom%20for%20the%20next%20two%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%24500%20a%20night%2C%20I%20had%20prime%20views%20of%20the%20falls%20from%20the%20moment%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20second%20I%20fell%20asleep.%20It%20was%20definitely%20worth%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Sheraton%20Fallsview%20is%20a%20popular%20hotel%20that%20faces%20Niagara%20Falls%20on%20the%20Canadian%20side%2C%20making%20it%20an%20exceptional%20place%20to%20stay%20if%20you%20want%20to%20enjoy%20front-row%20views%20at%20every%20turn.%3Cfig