newsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-fire-at-coaching-centre-in-lucknow-students-jump-from-1st-floor-11670747%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-fire-at-coaching-centre-in-lucknow-students-jump-from-1st-floor-11670747%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20hot%20new%20dating%20scene%20isn't%20a%20bar.%20It's%20Hyrox.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223564%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hyrox%20athletes%20finish%20their%20race%20in%20NYC%20in%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3455eec7a58f814f0d44d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20nothing%20like%20having%20your%20(very%20sweaty)%20date%20carry%20you%20across%20the%20finish%20line.%3Cp%3ESportograf.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20runners%20sporting%20elaborate%20glittered%20braids%2C%20sweat-soaked%20headbands%2C%20and%20neon%20matching%20outfits%20zipped%20past%20a%20bright%20blue%20inflatable%20Red%20Bull%20tunnel%20earlier%20this%20month%20at%20a%20Hyrox%20race%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20huddled%20nearby%20in%20a%20sliver%20of%20shade%20with%20four%20other%20women%2C%20all%20of%20us%20in%20matching%20shorts%20and%20sports%20bras.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20minutes%2C%20each%20of%20us%20was%20called%20into%20the%20tunnel%20to%20meet%20our%20race%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20blind%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20roped%20myself%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-hyrox-race-training-exercises-uk-men-champion-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHyrox%3C%2Fa%3E%20partner-race%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bmixed%20doubles%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20a%20man%20and%20woman%20run%20laps%20together%20and%20take%20turns%20performing%20at%20strength%20stations.%20A%20man%20I'd%20never%20met%20before%20would%20be%20my%20teammate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20each%20woman%20was%20whisked%20away%20to%20be%20paired%20with%20their%20date%2C%20yes%2C%20a%20real%20romantic%20(well%2C%20kind%20of)%20date%2C%20it%20was%20finally%20my%20turn.%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20chute%20and%20faced%20the%20start%20line.%20A%20hand%20tapped%20my%20shoulder%2C%20and%20I%20awkwardly%20turned%20around%20to%20meet%20Eric%2C%20a%20tall%2C%20dark-haired%20man%20with%20a%20cute%20smile%20and%20lean%20frame%20%E2%80%94%20and%20clearly%20a%20strong%20runner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20spring%2C%20my%20algorithm%20had%20figured%20me%20out.%20Sometime%20after%20liking%20every%20reel%20I%20saw%20of%20women%20seeking%20%26quot%3BHyrox%20husbands%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20started%20getting%20ads%20for%20Surf%2C%20a%20dating%20app%20for%20wellness-minded%20singles%2C%20and%20soon%20the%20company's%20reels%20teasing%20their%20novel%20Hyrox%20blind%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20called%20Surf%20to%20see%20if%20they'd%20be%20up%20for%20taking%20me%20on%20as%20a%2035-year-old%20single%20looking%20for%20love%20%E2%80%94%20and%20as%20a%20reporter%2C%20who'd%20document%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20best%20be%20summed%20up%20as%20a%2077-minute%2C%20sweat-soaked%20grind%20fueled%20by%20adrenaline%2C%20high-BPM%20club%20music%2C%20and%20maybe%20a%20little%20pride.%20But%20what%20made%20the%20experience%20memorable%20wasn't%20just%20the%20workout%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20meeting%20someone%20new%20and%20tackling%20the%20challenge%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b0f9231-9b92-40f4-83fc-9564ad8f0df6%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBaby%2C%20where%20the%20hell%20is%20my%20husband%3F%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnderneath%20the%20tunnel%20in%20our%20branded%20outfits%20(for%20which%2C%20along%20with%20my%20race%20ticket%2C%20I%20reimbursed%20the%20company)%2C%20it%20was%20obvious%20Surf%20had%20selected%20people%20already%20immersed%20in%20fitness%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDUtJAsSjBus%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDUtJAsSjBus%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDUtJAsSjBus%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Alina%20%7C%20Fitness%20Coach%20%E2%80%A2%20Qatar%20(%40alinamini.co)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20single%20employee%20sifted%20through%20more%20than%205%2C000%20applications%20for%20the%20New%20York%20event%2C%20using%20social%20media%20profiles%20to%20quickly%20gauge%20personality%20and%20fitness%20experience.%20With%20my%20account%20set%20to%20private%2C%20then%2C%20I%20likely%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20selected%20had%20I%20not%20called.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20sweltering%2089%20degrees%20along%20the%20Hudson%20River%2C%20and%20I%20was%20so%20keyed%20up%20that%2C%20with%20a%20David%20Guetta%20remix%20blaring%20nearby%2C%20I%20called%20Eric%20%26quot%3BAaron%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20headed%20to%20the%20nearby%20warm-up%20area%2C%20where%20we%20peppered%20each%20other%20with%20normal%20first-date%20questions%20about%20previous%20Hyrox%20experiences%20(his%20fourth%20race%20and%20my%20first)%20and%20work.%20Eric%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20from%20DC%2C%20gamely%20consented%20weeks%20prior%20to%20his%20blind%20date%20being%20a%20working%20reporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20other%20teams%20rehearsed%20sandbag%20handoffs%20for%20lunges%2C%20stretched%20out%20their%20legs%20on%20rows%20of%20treadmills%2C%20or%20loosened%20up%20their%20joints%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20Eric%20helped%20me%20refine%20ski-erg%20technique%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20almost%20no%20practice%20with%20the%20machine%20that%20mimics%20cross-country%20skiing.%20And%20it's%20not%20exactly%20intuitive%20to%20use.%20Feeling%20self-conscious%20about%20my%20awkward%20form%2C%20I%20eagerly%20accepted%20his%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20told%20me%20he%20had%20signed%20up%20for%20the%20race%20after%20finding%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20community%20through%20his%20track%20club%20and%20gym%2C%20something%20I%20was%20also%20keen%20to%20discover.%20His%20remote%20job%20in%20video%20editing%20pushed%20him%20to%20seek%20friends%20in%20fitness%2C%20a%20sphere%20he%20already%20loved%2C%20and%20later%20led%20him%20to%20coaching%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20absurd%2C%20or%2C%20as%20my%20friends%20said%2C%20like%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20reality%20TV%20show%2C%20but%20a%20fitness%20blind%20date%20in%202026%20made%20a%20ton%20of%20sense%20to%20me.%20I%20swing%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-dating-apps-ai-matchmakers-technology-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eswearing%20off%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20anxiously%20redownloading%20them%20later.%20I'm%20a%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20singles%20looking%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-find-compatible-partner-dating-app-fatigue-researcher-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein-person%20connections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20romantic%20or%20otherwise.%20Plus%2C%20fitness%20is%20important%20to%20me%2C%20and%20I%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20meeting%20a%20partner%20who%20can%20also%20crush%20back%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impulse%20behind%20a%20fitness%20blind%20date%20isn't%20exactly%20new%2C%20Dr.%20Jess%20Carbino%2C%20a%20sociologist%20formerly%20employed%20by%20Bumble%20and%20Tinder%2C%20told%20me%20days%20before%20the%20race.%20People%20have%20long%20sought%20partners%20within%20communities%20that%20reflect%20their%20identities%20and%20values%2C%20whether%20religious%2C%20political%2C%20or%20increasingly%2C%20lifestyle-based.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%26quot%3Blifestyle%20compatibility%26quot%3B%20becomes%20more%20important%20for%20some%2C%20gyms%20and%20run%20clubs%20have%20become%20essential%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-epidemic-decline-in-third-places-friends-parks-community-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethird%20spaces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Carbino%20said%2C%20where%20people%20connect%20over%20shared%20interests%20and%20can%20see%20prospective%20dates'%20discipline%20and%20social%20skills%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20helped%20inspire%20Surf's%20blind%20dates%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Rob%20Long%20said.%20As%20dating-app%20fatigue%20grows%2C%20more%20singles%20are%20looking%20for%20partners%20who%20may%20already%20share%20a%20meaningful%20part%20of%20their%20lives.%20Hyrox%2C%20he%20explained%2C%20offered%20a%20hyper-concentration%20of%20people%20united%20by%20a%20major%20interest%3A%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hyrox%20athlete%20cheers%20her%20partner.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a346b94c7a58f814f0d45fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20first%20dates%20don't%20offer%20the%20opportunity%20to%20watch%20your%20date%20slay%20a%20ski-erg%20machine.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Surf%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there's%20something%20%26quot%3Baspirational%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20meeting%20your%20partner%20at%20a%20Hyrox%2C%20Carbino%20said%2C%20after%20I'd%20told%20her%20some%20couples'%20races%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDZsV7AIxDvv%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaptured%20for%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20hopeful.%20They%20want%20to%20fantasize%20that%20things%20will%20work%20out%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20me%2C%20silently%20raising%20my%20hand%20as%20I%20heard%20this.%20Apparently%2C%20I%20wasn't%20the%20only%20one%20who%20found%20the%20idea%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221af2bd6e-9748-460f-b535-1d917aa5039e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESweat%2C%20sparkle%2C%20and%20sled%20pushes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20haven't%20heard%2C%20Hyrox%20is%20a%20fitness%20competition%20that%20started%20in%20Germany%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Now%2C%20the%20company%20stages%20events%20in%20more%20than%2085%20cities%20and%20estimates%20show%20roughly%20650%2C000%20competitors%20a%20year.%20I%20only%20learned%20about%20it%20after%20meeting%20a%20very%20handsome%20Australian%20Hyrox'er%20visiting%20the%20US%20over%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20race%20alternates%20one-kilometer%20runs%20with%20strength%20stations%20such%20as%20sled%20pushes%2C%20lunges%2C%20wall%20balls%2C%20rowing%2C%20and%20burpees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20at%20the%20variety%20of%20fitness%20levels%20in%20the%20race.%20Before%20arriving%2C%20insiders%20told%20me%20Hyrox's%20appeal%20lies%20partly%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20challenging%20without%20being%20reserved%20only%20for%20elite%20athletes.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyrox-founder-races-separate-normal-people-greek-statues-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erequires%20less%20speed%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20strength%20than%20events%20like%20marathons%20or%20competitive%20CrossFit.%20The%20hardest%20part%20might%20just%20be%20getting%20to%20a%20race.%20Events%20are%20relatively%20scarce%2C%20with%20tickets%2C%20costing%20around%20%24200%2C%20selling%20out%20in%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there%20was%20an%20electric%20atmosphere.%20It%20felt%20less%20like%20a%20race%20and%20more%20like%20a%20workout%20party%2C%20with%20alcohol%20swapped%20for%20cold-press%20juices.%20Sweating%20among%20throngs%20of%20people%20while%20a%20DJ%20blares%20music%C2%A0sounds%20like%20a%20perfect%20nightmare%20to%20me%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebut%20I%20ended%20up%20loving%20it.%20There%20were%20free%20hair-braiding%20stations%2C%20women%20sporting%20rave-style%20face%20sparkles%2C%20a%20nonalcoholic%20beer%20push-up%20challenge%2C%20and%20even%20a%20cold%20plunge.%20Merch%20was%20everywhere%2C%20including%20a%20Puma%20store%2C%20and%20tables%20brimmed%20with%20protein%20bars%2C%20creatine%2C%20sleep%20supplements%2C%20and%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20athletes%20preparing%20for%20a%20Hyrox%20event%20with%20colored%20lights%20and%20a%20fog%20machine%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea33e73fecbb42897a32a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHyrox%20took%20off%20in%20Europe%20and%20elsewhere%20before%20catching%20on%20in%20the%20US.%20Here%2C%20athletes%20begin%20a%20race%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20Thailand%2C%20on%20March%2021%2C%202026.%3Cp%3EAmaury%20PAUL%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20lifelong%20weightlifter%20and%20Marine%20veteran%2C%20but%20having%20a%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-hiit-short-workouts-boost-fitness-longevity-stroke-survival-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHIIT%20workouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20regular%20runs%20with%20just%20two%20months%20to%20prep%20%E2%80%94%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20more%20fun%20and%20addictive%20than%20I'd%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20overestimated%20how%20intimidating%20Hyrox%20would%20be.%20Social%20media%20led%20me%20to%20expect%20a%20sea%20of%20impossible%20fitness%20standards.%20While%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20racers%20I%20assumed%20were%20pros%20with%20washboard%20abs%2C%20I%20met%20mostly%20first-timers%2C%20fans%20whooping%20for%20their%20competing%20parents%20or%20spouses%2C%20and%20many%20who%20were%20less%20interested%20in%20winning%20and%20more%20so%20there%20for%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20experience%2C%20most%20mixed%20doubles%20teams%20enter%20Hyrox%20with%20some%20strategy%2C%20dividing%20the%20work%20according%20to%20each%20partner's%20strengths%20and%20managing%20muscle%20fatigue.%20A%20man%20might%20spend%20a%20few%20extra%20meters%20behind%20the%20335-pound%20sled%2C%20giving%20his%20partner's%20legs%20a%20break.%20Later%2C%20she%20might%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20the%20rower%20while%20he%20recovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20and%20I%20strategized%20while%20dousing%20ourselves%20in%20sunscreen%20under%20the%20warm-up%20tent%2C%20agreeing%20that%20as%20the%20slower%20partner%2C%20I'd%20set%20our%20run%20pace%20(but%20there%20was%20no%20universe%20in%20which%20I%20was%20going%20to%20let%20my%20date%20do%20all%20the%20heavy%20lifting).%20We'd%20start%20easy%2C%20staying%20safe%20in%20the%20heat.%20I'd%20spent%20the%20previous%20two%20days%20downing%20water%20and%20electrolytes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-your-own-electrolyte-drink-for-better-hydration-dietitian-recipe-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earrive%20hydrated%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plus%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20my%20date%20as%20we%20ran%20around%20the%20pier%20jutting%20into%20the%20Hudson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20changed%20four%20laps%20in%2C%20when%2C%20after%20talking%20about%20work%2C%20families%2C%20and%20this%20story%2C%20Eric%20told%20me%20our%20one-mile%20pace%20was%20around%209%20minutes%2C%20which%20sounded%20slow%20to%20me%20and%20Eric%2C%20who%20can%20comfortably%20run%2010%20miles%20without%20stopping.%20We%20could%20go%20faster%2C%20he%20said%20gently%2C%20and%20maybe%20even%20finish%20within%20a%20respectable%20one%20hour%20and%2020%20minutes%2C%20but%20I'd%20have%20to%20lay%20off%20the%20yapping%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20lock-in.%20I%20giggled%2C%20but%20felt%20a%20switch%20flip%2C%20wanting%20the%20challenge.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20old%20military%20hikes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D970362212054522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvival%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20discomfort%20is%20normal%2C%20even%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Placeholder%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3472bcf4bed3c6152cbfdf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECompetitors%20can%20race%20as%20a%20relay%20team%20of%20four%2C%20a%20pair%2C%20or%20solo%2C%20as%20pictured%20above.%20Mixed%20doubles%20uses%20men's%20open%20weights%2C%20meaning%20women%20compete%20at%20the%20women's%20pro%20standard.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Baker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEric's%20experience%20having%20done%20a%20handful%20of%20Hyroxes%20meant%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20feel%20lost%2C%20as%20long%20as%20I%20could%20stay%20close%20enough%20to%20dive%20from%20the%20high-traffic%20track%20and%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20event%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BRoxzone%26quot%3B%20maze%2C%20where%20scores%20of%20athletes%20shuffle%20from%20laps%20to%20their%20progressive%20strength%20stations.%20At%20the%20sled-pull%20station%2C%20I%20tripped%20and%20fell%20twice%20%E2%80%94%20each%20time%20Eric%20helped%20me%20up%2C%20both%20of%20us%20laughing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22016acf20-9990-4a8b-8a77-71a278e01137%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpeed%20dating%20(to%20the%20finish%20line)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20would%20anyone%20look%20for%20love%20while%20sweating%20under%20the%20hot%20NYC%20sun%3F%20One%20expert%20said%20it's%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20shared%20challenge%20that's%20most%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20sort%20of%20'good%20friction'%20that%20makes%20us%20value%20how%20we%20spend%20our%20time%20and%20gives%20us%20meaning%20in%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Easter%2C%20whose%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Comfort%20Crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20explores%20why%20people%20enjoy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frucking-longevity-burn-fat-build-muscle-no-gym-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrueling%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me%20after%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESedentary%20lifestyles%20and%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-meta-apple-wearables-phone-addiction-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edependence%20on%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20eroded%20opportunities%20to%20hone%20grit%20and%20endurance%2C%20he%20continued.%20The%20best%20remedy%20is%20usually%20some%20type%20of%20shared%20suffering%20that%20deepens%20bonds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sort%20of%20teaches%20people%20that%20%5Bthey%5D%20are%20more%20capable%20than%20they%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20Easter%20said%20of%20challenges%20like%20Hyrox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heat%20was%20my%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20and%20what%20I%20was%20most%20anxious%20about.%20The%20military%20is%20fanatical%20about%20hydration%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fheat-exhaustion-symptoms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheat%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20good%20reason.%20Later%2C%20some%20racers%20online%20noted%20several%20apparent%20heat%20injuries%20among%20fellow%20competitors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyrox%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20my%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20heat%20injury%20rates%20before%20publication.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20the%20military%20at%2023%20to%20challenge%20myself%2C%20and%20haven't%20found%20a%20similarly%20rewarding%20experience%20since%20my%20early%20days%20as%20a%20lieutenant.%20I'd%20met%20another%20veteran%20a%20day%20prior%2C%20cheering%20on%20his%20fianc%C3%A9%20as%20she%20blew%20through%20burpees.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%20leaving%20active%20duty%2C%20he'd%20found%20a%20new%20tribe%2C%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eric%20and%20I%20made%20up%20some%20time%20after%20all%20my%20yapping%20and%20finished%20within%201%20hours%20and%2020%20minutes.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3460e20e60dfb3f373f67e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEric%20and%20I%20made%20up%20some%20time%20after%20all%20my%20yapping%20and%20finished%20just%20under%201%20hour%20and%2017%20minutes.%3Cp%3ESportograf.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Marine%20Corps%20is%20famously%20cultish%2C%20and%20Hyrox%20might%20not%20be%20far%20off.%20Plus%2C%20seeing%20how%20someone%20treats%20you%20when%20they're%20spent%20but%20there's%20still%20100%20wall%20balls%20to%20go%20is%20pretty%20cool.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20too%20wiped%20to%20encourage%20him%20really%20anywhere%20(%26quot%3BI'm%20clapping%20for%20you%20in%20my%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20panted%20to%20him)%2C%20but%20Eric%20gallantly%20cheered%20me%20on%20everywhere.%20At%20each%20water%20stop%2C%20he%20never%20drank%20until%20he%20made%20sure%20I%20had%20a%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20crossed%20the%20finish%20line%20%E2%80%94%20he%20asked%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20cross%20it%20on%20his%20back%2C%20and%20I%20gladly%20accepted%20%E2%80%94%20and%20afterward%2C%20we%20collapsed%20into%20zero-gravity%20chairs%20reserved%20for%20tired%20racers%2C%20easing%20the%20pressure%20off%20of%20tired%20joints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitting%20there%2C%20sweaty%20and%20crusted%20with%20cheap%20sunscreen%20and%20a%20lopsided%20ballcap%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20this%20was%20the%20least%20awkward%20first%20date%20I'd%20ever%20been%20on%2C%20even%20as%20my%20cheeks%20burned%20from%20the%20heat.%20There%20wasn't%20much%20room%20for%20pretense%20while%20surviving%20burpees%20through%20the%20heat.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20our%20heart%20rates%20returned%20to%20normal%2C%20I%20realized%20I'd%20learned%20more%20about%20Eric%20than%20I%20ever%20would%20have%20over%20a%20drink.%20And%20even%20when%20our%20race%20was%20over%2C%20we%20still%20had%20more%20yapping%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-went-on-a-blind-date-at-hyrox-fun-sweaty-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782130381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a38821ef4bed3c6152cc6d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-went-on-a-blind-date-at-hyrox-fun-sweaty-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20never%20thought%20I'd%20have%20a%20blind%20date%20at%20Hyrox%2C%20but%20I%20met%20a%20guy%20and%20did%20a%20good%20workout.%20It's%20part%20of%20a%20trend%20that%20focuses%20on%20lifestyle%20compatibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JD%20Vance%20Says%20US%20May%20Unfreeze%20Some%20Iranian%20Assets%2C%20Hints%20At%20Successful%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22JD%20Vance's%20comments%20came%20after%20he%20a