Das%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22308ded9e-92ac-4fd7-9b9e-e1afc0b18203%5C%22%3E'The%20craft%20they%20loved%20is%20dead'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDas'%20comments%20tap%20into%20a%20growing%20debate%20over%20how%20AI%20coding%20tools%20are%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-agents-tools-software-engineering-jobs-future-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereshaping%20software%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20theme%20at%20the%20center%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20latest%20series%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fthe-great-coding-reset%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Great%20Coding%20Reset%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20companies%20encourage%20developers%20to%20generate%20more%20code%20with%20AI%2C%20some%20engineers%20say%20their%20role%20is%20shifting%20from%20writing%20software%20to%20reviewing%2C%20managing%2C%20and%20validating%20machine-generated%20work%20%E2%80%94%20a%20change%20that%20is%20forcing%20some%20to%20rethink%20where%20their%20value%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broader%20problem%20is%20what%20Business%20Insider's%20Amanda%20Hoover%20recently%20described%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwelcome-age-ai-sprawl-too-many-tools-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20sprawl%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3A%20workers%20juggling%20multiple%20AI%20tools%2C%20duplicating%20work%2C%20and%20generating%20ever-increasing%20volumes%20of%20output%20without%20clear%20evidence%20that%20companies%20are%20becoming%20substantially%20more%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20craftsmen%20are%20tired.%20Very%20tired%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20burden%20of%20review%20falls%20on%20the%20craftsman.%20The%20burden%20of%20understanding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20makes%20code%20generation%20easier%2C%20reviewing%20and%20maintaining%20that%20code%2