%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frebel-bjp-leader-defeats-eknath-sinde-nominee-in-maharashtra-council-polls-11670400%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frebel-bjp-leader-defeats-eknath-sinde-nominee-in-maharashtra-council-polls-11670400%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SharkNinja's%20CEO%20worried%20workers%20were%20falling%20behind%20on%20AI.%20So%20he%20decided%20to%20'shock%20the%20system.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SharkNinja%20Hackathon%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32f9052bbd1d834ef251d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELocal%20college%20students%20participate%20in%20SharkNinja's%20recent%20hackathon%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BJailbreak.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ETony%20Luong%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20was%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20called%20over%20a%20recent%20hire%20from%20another%20team%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20SharkNinja's%20emerging%20AI%20power%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20about%2090%20minutes%2C%20he%20had%20built%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20automated%20a%20cumbersome%20process%20for%20tracking%20projects%20and%20holding%20teams%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWord%20of%20the%20worker's%20feat%20spread%20beyond%20the%20group%20gathered%20around%20him%20in%20an%20office%20at%20the%20company's%20headquarters%20near%20Boston%2C%20said%20SharkNinja%20CEO%20Mark%20Barrocas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Barrocas%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20nearly%20two%20decades%20helping%20transform%20the%20company%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efrom%20an%20infomercial-era%20curiosity%20into%20a%20consumer-products%20juggernaut%2C%20the%20moment%20captured%20something%20larger%20happening%20inside%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20the%20great%20equalizer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20you're%20a%20college%20kid%20or%20a%20senior%20vice%20president.%20You%20actually%20can%20contribute%20at%20a%20similar%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Barrocas%20worried%20that%20too%20few%20employees%20were%20experiencing%20that%20AI%20breakthrough.%20Some%20workers%20had%20gone%20all%20in%20on%20the%20technology%2C%20while%20others%20seemed%20to%20be%20hanging%20back.%20To%20close%20the%20gap%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20%26quot%3Bshock%20the%20system%26quot%3B%20by%20largely%20pausing%20normal%20work%20and%20immersing%20the%20company%20in%20a%20four-day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-hackathons-ai-talent-big-tech-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20hackathon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdown%20was%20an%20unprecedented%20move%20at%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20TikTok-famous%20Ninja%20Creami%20ice%20cream%20maker%20and%20Justin%20Bieber-backed%20Shark%20ChillPill%20personal%20cooler.%20Four%20days%20in%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20company%20was%20hurtling%20toward%20a%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20uncharted%20territories%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrocas%20said%20during%20the%20hack.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20idea%20what's%20going%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22569260a1-a13b-4a0c-97d5-0d5d4f2385c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'If%20it%20ain't%20broke%2C%20break%20it'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20SharkNinja's%20headquarters%2C%20where%20vacuum%20handles%20poke%20above%20cubicle%20walls%20like%20reeds%20in%20a%20marsh%2C%20leaders%20assembled%20teams%20of%20roughly%2010%20to%2015%20employees%20from%20across%20the%20company%20to%20tackle%20about%2020%20major%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20springtime%20event%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BJailbreak%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20bigger%20version%20of%20the%20hacks%20the%20company%20began%20hosting%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBosses%20encouraged%20employees%20whose%20work%20didn't%20require%20much%20coordination%20across%20teams%20to%20come%20up%20with%20challenges%20for%20their%20own%20departments%2C%20resulting%20in%20about%20400%20additional%20projects%2C%20Barrocas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20mark%20the%20week%2C%20a%20giant%20banner%20hanging%20in%20a%20two-story%20lobby%20atrium%20declared%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20ain't%20broke%2C%20break%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228006%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SharkNinja%20Hackathon%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32f9664074dae0e2045244%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225337%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20banner%20at%20an%20entrance%20to%20SharkNinja's%20headquarters%20hit%20on%20the%20week's%20hack%20theme.%3Cp%3ETony%20Luong%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20business%20worked%20side%20by%20side%20on%20projects%2C%20sometimes%20with%20colleagues%20they%20had%20never%20met.%20Dozens%20of%20college%20students%20from%20the%20Boston%20area%20also%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ejoined%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20a%20related%20event%20designed%20to%20develop%20participants'%20skills%20and%20help%20SharkNinja%20spot%20potential%20recruits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20to%20identify%20practical%20ways%20the%20company%20could%20weave%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-waiting-ai-productivity-boom-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20into%20its%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20product%20development%20and%20marketing%20to%20supply%20chain%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20group%20demonstrated%20tools%20that%20could%20mine%20consumer%20feedback%20from%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20including%20from%20social%20media%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sort%20it%20by%20country%20or%20demographic%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20team%20spent%20part%20of%20the%20week%20using%20AI%20to%20generate%20ideas%20and%20prototypes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20build%20%E2%80%94%20two%20new%20products%2C%20connect%20them%20to%20the%20cloud%2C%20and%20build%20accompanying%20apps%20populated%20with%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20used%20to%20take%20months%20and%20quarters%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20is%20now%20taking%20a%20matter%20of%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20conference-room%20table%2C%20laptops%20crowded%20around%20a%20cluster%20of%20water%20bottles.%20Down%20the%20hall%2C%20Shark%20fans%20and%20air%20purifiers%20hummed%20at%20full%20blast%20inside%20a%20packed%20meeting%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SharkNinja%20Hackathon%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32fb08564c774507cd3fc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20project%20brought%20together%20product%20developers%20and%20marketers%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20makes%20products%20go%20viral.%3Cp%3ETony%20Luong%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20group%20worked%20on%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20could%20rate%20product%20concepts%20and%20suggest%20improvements%20by%20analyzing%20factors%20such%20as%20consumer%20demand%2C%20manufacturing%20feasibility%2C%20and%20business%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20matters%20because%20the%20company%2C%20whose%20sales%20rose%20to%20nearly%20%246.4%20billion%20last%20year%2C%20typically%20introduces%2025%20products%20a%20year%2C%20including%20the%20viral%20hits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-flexstyle-amazon-deal-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20FlexStyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20hair-styling%20gadget%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-at-costco-this-month-according-to-employee-2025-6%23the-ninja-slushi-is-perfect-for-making-frozen-drinks-at-home-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENinja%20Slushi%3C%2Fa%3E%20frozen-drink%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20week's%20AI%20push%20wasn't%20limited%20to%20product%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Kaitlyn%20Hebert%2C%20CMO%20of%20global%20brands%2C%20a%20key%20project%20focused%20on%20nailing%20down%20what%20makes%20products%20break%20through%20on%20social%20media.%20For%20her%20group's%20hack%2C%20that%20meant%20bringing%20together%20product%20developers%20and%20marketers%20to%20build%20a%20repeatable%20playbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20believe%20virality%20is%20luck%2C%20but%20I%20think%20here%20we%20know%20how%20to%20design%20virality%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22faa3bdc6-9d3f-4a2d-91ee-8c67046baa2d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20hackathon%20instead%20of%20consultants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20Barrocas%20said%2C%20he%20kept%20hearing%20the%20same%20advice%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-consulting-mckinsey-pwc-deloitte-bcg-kpmg-accenture-ey-ibm-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBring%20in%20consultants%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20develop%20an%20AI%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20other%20leaders%2C%20he%20met%20with%20consulting%20firms%20and%20CEOs%20of%20tech%20companies.%20In%20those%20conversations%2C%20he%20joked%2C%20he%20would%20hear%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bagentic%26quot%3B%20several%20times%20in%20the%20same%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20Barrocas%20listened%2C%20the%20more%20skeptical%20he%20became%20that%20an%20army%20of%20consultants%20could%20tell%20SharkNinja%20how%20to%20use%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224647%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SharkNinja%20Hackathon%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a344d47c7a58f814f0d4441%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226970%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESharkNinja%20CEO%20Mark%20Barrocas%20said%20the%20company's%20job%20is%20to%20avoid%20leaving%20any%20worker%20behind%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%20know-how.%3Cp%3ETony%20Luong%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOdds%20are%20that%20strategy%20is%20outdated%2C%20you%20know%2C%20three%20months%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrocas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20started%20noticing%20that%20managers%20or%20senior%20managers%20were%20sharing%20different%20ways%20they%20were%20using%20AI%20to%20solve%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%2C%20'Who%20told%20you%20to%20do%20this%3F'%26quot%3B%20Barrocas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20say%2C%20'Nobody.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20weren't%20waiting%20for%20a%20corporate%20AI%20road%20map.%20That%20observation%20became%20the%20foundation%20for%20Jailbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20already%20had%20this%20culture%20here%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0what%20we%20call%20'finding%20problems%2C%20fixing%20problems%2C'%26quot%3B%20Barrocas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20employees%20suddenly%20have%20a%20new%20set%20of%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20year%20or%20two%20ago%2C%20you%20would%20say%2C%20'Oh%2C%20well%2C%20IT%20has%20to%20fix%20the%20system%2C'%26quot%3B%20Barrocas%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20it's%20like%2C%20'I%20have%20a%20problem.%20I%20can%20fix%20the%20problem.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20Jailbreak%20wasn't%20simply%20to%20build%20tools%20using%20AI.%20It%20was%20to%20get%20the%20company's%20roughly%204%2C000%20workers%20to%20adapt%20and%20move%20in%20the%20same%20direction%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrocas%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20to%20not%20leave%20anyone%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22667bdfa6-c879-49bc-bfd5-35cf6ac7b943%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech-startup%20energy%2C%20appliance-company%20roots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20week%2C%20the%20atmosphere%20became%20festival-like%3A%20Balloons%20climbed%20stair%20railings%20and%20framed%20doorways.%20In%20a%20common%20area%2C%20a%20display%20that%20looked%20like%20a%20massive%20Lite-Brite%20glowed%20with%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BJailbreak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENear%20a%20lobby%2C%20beauty%20teams%20offered%20touch-ups%20using%20SharkNinja%20products%20to%20workers%20who%20wanted%20a%20professional%20photographer%20to%20take%20their%20headshots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228064%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SharkNinja%20Hackathon%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32fa7a564c774507cd3fbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorkers%20had%20opportunities%20to%20play%20mini-golf%20and%20other%20games%20during%20Jailbreak.%3Cp%3ETony%20Luong%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20lunchtime%2C%20some%20workers%20drifted%20outside%20to%20food%20trucks%20brought%20in%20for%20the%20event%2C%20while%20others%20filed%20into%20Sharkcuterie%2C%20a%20cafeteria%20named%20after%20an%20employee's%20winning%20contest%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuge%20Connect%20Four%2C%20Jenga%2C%20and%20chess%20installations%20stood%20in%20hallways%20and%20in%20common%20areas.%20In%20one%2C%20handfuls%20of%20workers%20traversed%20a%20mini-golf%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20atmosphere%20was%20lively%2C%20yet%20the%20stakes%20were%20high.%20SharkNinja%20is%20awarding%20%241%20million%20in%20prizes%20in%202026%20to%20workers%20or%20groups%20of%20workers%20who%20develop%20big%20AI%20ideas.%20It's%20already%20cut%20%2420%2C000%20bonus%20checks%20for%20several%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20dozens%20of%20product-development%20labs%20off-limits%20to%20visitors%2C%20in%20a%20central%20hallway%2C%20a%20coffee%20maker%20and%20a%20bladeless%20tower%20fan%20sat%20on%20pedestals%20under%20spotlights%2C%20like%20exhibits%20in%20a%20museum%20devoted%20to%20home%20gadgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20company%20that%20sells%20blenders%20and%20vacuums%20rather%20than%20software%2C%20the%20atmosphere%20felt%20closer%20to%20that%20of%20a%20tech%20giant%20than%20to%20a%20traditional%20consumer-products%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarrocas%20said%20he%20doesn't%20want%20AI%20expertise%20concentrated%20among%20a%20handful%20of%20enthusiasts.%20He%20wants%20thousands%20of%20employees%20to%20experiment%20with%20the%20technology%20and%20figure%20out%20how%20it%20could%20improve%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20a%20tech%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrocas%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20problem-solving%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsharkninjas-big-bet-4-day-ai-hackathon-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782121381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32f92f4074dae0e204523f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsharkninjas-big-bet-4-day-ai-hackathon-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SharkNinja%20didn't%20hire%20consultants%20to%20solve%20its%20AI%20challenge.%20Instead%2C%20it%20shut%20down%20normal%20work%20for%20four%20days%20and%20told%20employees%20to%20start%20hacking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Keir%20Starmer%20Resigned%3A%20Behind%20UK's%206th%20Premature%20PM%20Exit%20In%2010%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Labour%20Party%20MPs%20had%20been%20discontent%20over%20a%20popularity%20decline%20since%20Starmer%20took%20office%20following%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20July%202024.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782121201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-keir-starmer-resigned-behind-uks-6th-premature-pm-exit-in-10-years-11670437%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Labour%20Party%20MPs%20had%20been%20discontent%20over%20a%20popularity%20decline%20since%20Star