Url%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic's%20engineering%20leader%20says%20Claude%20Code%20is%20making%20programmers%20lonelier%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223435%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Branding%20for%20Claude%20Code%20on%20removable%20posters%20at%20Anthropic%20PBC's%20Code%20with%20Claude%20developer%20conference.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a383c65c7a58f814f0d4cd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20agents%20are%20making%20a%20solitary%20job%20even%20lonelier.%3Cp%3EChris%20Ratcliffe%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic's%20engineering%20leader%2C%20Fiona%20Fung%2C%20says%20Claude%20Code%20allows%20her%20team%20to%20ship%20way%20more%20code.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20it%20has%20also%20made%20her%20employees%2C%20who%20now%20work%20mostly%20with%20AI%20agents%2C%20lonelier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFung%20said%20the%20antidote%20is%20to%20create%20more%20opportunities%20for%20engineers%20to%20collaborate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECoding%20is%20famously%20a%20solitary%20job.%20AI%20agents%20have%20only%20made%20it%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiona%20Fung%2C%20an%20engineering%20leader%20at%20Anthropic%20who%20runs%20the%20teams%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-code-creator-advice-cs-grads-startup-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Claude%20Cowork%2C%20said%20her%20team%20noticed%20that%20as%20engineers%20relied%20more%20on%20AI%20agents%2C%20they%20became%20more%20isolated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20that%20we%20found%20interesting%20on%20the%20Claude%20Code%20team%20is%2C%20after%20a%20while%2C%20we%20felt%20it%20could%20start%20being%20a%20lonely%20experience%20because%20we%20all%20started%20just%20working%20with%20our%20agents%20so%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said%20on%20the%20latest%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BLenny's%20Podcast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20problem%2C%20Fung's%20team%20tried%20to%20restore%20some%20of%20what%20agentic%20coding%20had%20begun%20to%20erase.%20They%20began%20organizing%20programming%20lunches%2C%20hackathons%2C%20and%20blocks%20of%20shared%20%26quot%3Bmaker%20time%26quot%3B%20so%20engineers%20could%20work%20near%20one%20another%20and%20learn%20from%20each%20other's%20AI%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20uses%20Claude%20Cowork.%20Everybody%20uses%20a%20flow%20so%20differently%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20do%20pairwise%20programming%2C%20we%20actually%20learn%20so%20much%20from%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude%20Code%20has%20quickly%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20used%20products%20in%20software%20development.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-startups-claude-has-already-won-the-ai-coding-wars-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esurvey%20conducted%20by%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20founders%20and%20venture%20capitalists%2C%20Claude%20Code%20emerged%20as%20the%20dominant%20AI%20coding%20tool%20inside%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estartups.%20Some%20founders%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esay%20it%20has%20become%20their%20default%20for%20complex%20engineering%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%20are%20now%20spending%20more%20time%20directing%20agents%2C%20reviewing%20outputs%2C%20and%20orchestrating%20parallel%20tasks.%20The%20rise%20of%20vibecoding%2C%20where%20people%20use%20natural%20language%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-guide-prompt-engineering-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprompt%20and%20build%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20also%20allowed%20nontechnical%20founders%20to%20create%20custom%20tools%20without%20hiring%20traditional%20engineering%20teams%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bsolopreneur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20can%20get%20lonely%2C%20however%2C%20and%20many%20founders%20swear%20by%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFung%20said%20that%20is%20why%20her%20team%20has%20focused%20on%20creating%20more%20opportunities%20for%20engineers%20to%20work%20side%20by%20side%2C%20even%20though%20they%20use%20AI%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20I%20watch%20someone%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20learn%20something%20myself%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-code-ai-engineering-loneliness-fiona-fung%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782121141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a383c65c7a58f814f0d4cd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-code-ai-engineering-loneliness-fiona-fung%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fiona%20Fung%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20teams%20behind%20Claude%20Code%20and%20Cowork%2C%20says%20AI%20agents%20are%20making%20her%20teams%20lonelier.%20She%20has%20some%20solutions%20to%20the%20problem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Quentin%20Tarantino%2C%20Kylie%20Minogue%20to%20Star%20in%20New%20Jamie%20Adams%20Film%20From%20Visor%20Entertainment%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782120953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236786987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Quentin%20Tarantino%20has%20reunited%20with%20Welsh%20helmer%20Jamie%20Adams%2C%20known%20for%20his%20Nouvelle%20Vague-inspired%20improvised%20filmmaking%20style%2C%20on%20a%20new%20feature%20project%20in%20which%20the%20iconic%20%E2%80%9CKill%20Bill%E2%80%9D%20director%20will%20again%20step%20in%20front