r%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGrocery%20chains%20have%20been%20leaning%20into%20ready-to-eat%20foods%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20aims%20to%20meet%20demand%20from%20time-stretched%20shoppers%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20pay%20restaurant%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20compromise%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20groceries%2C%20but%20cheaper%20than%20eating%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20is%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20that's%20sometimes%20the%20thinking%20when%20opting%20for%20a%20quick%20meal%20from%20a%20restaurant%20or%20ordering%20delivery%20instead%20of%20shopping%20for%20groceries%20and%20cooking%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaught%20between%20busy%20schedules%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-restaurant-prices-arent-dropping-lower-inflation-labor-costs-mcdonalds-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erising%20restaurant%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20US%20shoppers%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20compromise%20%E2%80%94%20and%20grocery%20stores%20are%20selling%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20grocery%20chains%20are%20now%20offering%20some%20sort%20of%20freshly%20prepared%20options%20for%20shoppers%20who%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20cook%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20spring%20for%20restaurant%20food.%20(Plus%2C%20they%20can%20stock%20up%20on%20groceries%20during%20the%20trip.)%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhole-foods-daily-shop-visit-small-but-efficient-selection-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhole%20Foods%20hot%20bar%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20to%20get%20in%20on%20this%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20actively%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20customers%20to%20stretch%20their%20budgets%20through%20solutions%20like%20our%20meals%2C%26quot%3B%20Walmart%20US%20CEO%20David%20Guggina%20said%20at%20a%20recent%20investor%20conference.%20He%20said%20the%20store's%20ready-to-eat%20meals%2C%20like%20its%20rotisserie%20chicken%20and%20two%20sides%2C%20can%20feed%20a%20family%20of%20four%20for%20under%20%2410.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20data%20show%20that%20restaurant%20prices%20have%20been%20steadily%20rising%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20while%20grocery%20prices%20have%20been%20more%20stable%2C%20apart%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fcoffee-prices-food-inflation-climate-change-eggs-bank-of-america-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20few%20painful%20bumps%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FFAiL3%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FFAiL3%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20McKinsey%20out%20this%20month%20highlighted%20the%20shift%20from%20restaurants%20to%20ready-to-eat%20grocery%20store%20meals%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%20themes%20reshaping%20the%20grocery%20industry%20right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20up%20there%20with%20heavy%20hitters%20like%20e-commerce%2C%20retail%20media%2C%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrepared%20foods%20are%20competing%20directly%20with%20restaurants%20for%20meal%20occasions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BRoughly%20one-quarter%20of%20all%20consumers%20report%20purchasing%20grocery-prepared%20foods%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20ordering%20from%20restaurants%2C%20most%20often%20replacing%20quick-service%20and%20fast-casual%20occasions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20is%20even%20more%20pronounced%20among%20younger%20customers%2C%20ages%2018%20to%2029%2C%20the%20report%20found%2C%20and%20prepared%20foods%20were%20by%20far%20the%20leading%20driver%20of%20trip%20frequency%20across%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20warehouse%20chains%2C%20which%20are%20not%20unlike%20oversize%20grocery%20stores%2C%20are%20in%20on%20the%20game%2C%20not%20just%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-rotisserie-chicken-to-buy-grocery-stores-review-comparison-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%245%20chickens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20also%20platters%20of%20mac%20and%20cheese%2C%20enchiladas%2C%20taco%20kits%2C%20and%20sushi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam's%20Club%20told%20reporters%20in%20Bentonville%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20its%20recent%20expansion%20of%20fresh%20options%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-ai-changing-how-people-work-shop-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edriven%20by%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20time%20to%20cook%20and%20that%20restaurants%20are%20too%20pricey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Walmart-owned%20chain%20is%20also%20rolling%20out%20a%20program%20where%20it%20will%20chop%20selections%20of%20fresh%20fruit%20for%20sale%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20typical%20party%20tray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-expands-spark-delivery-to-restaurant-orders-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrocery%20delivery%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20also%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20shifting%20restaurant%20habits.%20Several%20chains%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Walmart%2C%20Sam's%20Club%2C%20Costco%2C%20and%20others%20%E2%80%94%20now%20offer%20prepared%20options%20alongside%20their%20same-day%20fulfillment%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20speeds%20reaching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-sams-club-offers-enhanced-express-delivery-option-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20minutes%20or%20less%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20grocery%20stores%20are%20squarely%20in%20DoorDash%20or%20Uber%20Eats%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%