%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20customization%20is%20outdated%20and%20that%20you%20should%20craft%20a%20single%2C%20solid%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEffective%20networking%20is%20relational%2C%20not%20transactional%3B%20ask%20valuable%20questions%20to%20build%20connections.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40emily.the.recruiter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Durham%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%2030-year-old%20author%2C%20content%20creator%2C%20podcaster%2C%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20former%20recruiter%20who%20lives%20in%20Toronto.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20Emily%20The%20Recruiter%2C%20a%20content%20creator%20with%20nearly%20one%20million%20TikTok%20followers%2C%20I%20held%20a%20variety%20of%20recruitment%20roles%20for%20nearly%2010%20years.%20I%20worked%20at%20a%20couple%20of%20large%20banks%20and%20some%20large%20tech%20companies%2C%20and%20focused%20on%20all%20career%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20that%20early-career%20folks%20weren't%20passing%20interviews%20or%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20advocate%20for%20higher%20salaries.%20I%20would%20be%20on%20the%20phone%20with%20candidates%2C%20offering%20them%20a%20salary%2C%20and%20they'd%20say%2C%20OK%2C%20yeah%2C%20I'll%20take%20it.%20I'd%20then%20find%20myself%20egging%20them%20on%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20them%20to%20negotiate%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20prepare%20each%20candidate%20for%20every%20interview%20round%20the%20way%20I%20wanted%20to.%20One%20day%20in%202019%2C%20I%20recorded%20a%2030-minute%20podcast%20episode%20on%20how%20not%20to%20mess%20up%20an%20interview%20and%20how%20to%20negotiate.%20Within%20three%20weeks%2C%20it%20took%20off.%20From%20there%2C%20I%20posted%20to%20my%20podcast%2C%20Clock%20In%20with%20Emily%20Durham%2C%20regularly%2C%20and%20within%20the%20same%20year%2C%20to%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20content%20creation%20and%20recruiting%2C%20I%20was%20working%2075%20to%2080%20hours%20a%20week%20and%20sleeping%20only%20four%20hours%20a%20night%20%E2%80%94%20I%20knew%20something%20had%20to%20give.%20In%202024%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20to%20pursue%20content%20creation%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20advising%20my%20best%20friend%20%E2%80%94%20or%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20on%20how%20to%20navigate%20today's%20job%20market%2C%20these%20are%20the%2012%20tips%20I%20would%20give.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214aff58a-3657-4ed9-b2ad-53ee490b208b%5C%22%3E1.%20Don't%3A%20Customize%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20every%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20never%20customize%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20every%20job%20I'm%20applying%20to.%20I%20think%20it's%20incredibly%20dated%20advice%2C%20and%20it%20solves%20the%20wrong%20problem.%20The%20problem%20today%20is%20that%20no%20one's%20seeing%20it.%20You%20spend%20all%20this%20time%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20piece%20of%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Susie%20from%20HR%20won't%20be%20reading%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%20Often%2C%20people%20who%20customize%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20each%20time%20use%20AI%20to%20help%2C%20and%20everyone%20else%20does%2C%20too.%20You%20think%20it's%20standing%20out%2C%20but%20it's%20not.%20Recruiters%20can%20tell%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20has%20been%20touched%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b95a6ed7-b4a5-4d0d-87dd-7904fe685a08%5C%22%3E2.%20Do%3A%20Make%20one%20solid%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20having%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20you%20wrote%20stands%20out%20so%20much%20more%20than%20having%20a%20cookie-cutter%2C%20perfect%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20reads%20like%20all%20of%20the%20other%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20focus%20on%20having%20o%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecommendations-for-writing-a-great-resume-and-best-examples-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ene%20really%20solid%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'd%20look%20at%20the%20roles%20I%20truly%20want%20at%20my%20ideal%20companies%2C%20then%20examine%20the%20job%20descriptions%20and%20the%20recurring%20words.%20These%20would%20include%20technical%20skills%2C%20leadership%2C%20data%2C%20and%20analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I'd%20cross-reference%20it%20with%20two%20or%20three%20more%20job%20descriptions%20and%20see%20how%20many%20of%20those%20repeat.%20That's%20usually%20a%20good%20indicator%20of%20your%20keywords.%20If%20you're%20feeling%20super%20stuck%20or%20overwhelmed%2C%20you%20can%20also%20ask%20AI%20to%20validate%20the%20keywords%20you%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntegrate%20those%20keywords%20into%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20by%20making%20sure%20that%20they're%20included%20in%20how%20you%20describe%20your%20work.%20So%2C%20instead%20of%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20worked%20with%20spreadsheets%2C%26quot%3B%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20analyzed%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20now%20you%20actually%20have%20those%20qualifications%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20would%20also%20never%20catch%20me%20dead%20doing%20or%20recommending%20high-volume%20AI%20applications.%20The%20day%20I%20use%20an%20AI%20scraper%20to%20apply%20for%201%2C000%20jobs%20a%20day%2C%20I'll%20be%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229bb36ce5-982a-4a0d-99df-f8bfee05c615%5C%22%3E3.%20Don't%3A%20Treat%20networking%20like%20a%20transaction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20my%20one%20solid%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20I'd%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20time%20networking%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20in%20person%20so%20I'm%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-common-networking-mistake-2015-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebig%20networking%20mistake%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20treating%20it%20like%20a%20transaction.%20This%20can%20look%20like%20reaching%20out%20to%20someone%20you%20don't%20know%20and%20saying%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I'm%20Emily.%20I'm%20looking%20for%20a%20marketing%20role.%20Are%20you%20hiring%3F%20Can%20you%20refer%20me%3F%26quot%3B%20People%20aren't%20going%20to%20refer%20you%20because%20they%20don't%20know%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20probably%20get%20100%20of%20these%20messages%20a%20day.%20Because%20you%20think%20this%20is%20good%20outreach%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20refer%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236574572-518a-44bf-a31f-e70960c75b1e%5C%22%3E4.%20Do%3A%20Butter%20people%20up%20by%20asking%20valuable%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20need%20to%20feel%20like%20you're%20buttering%20them%20up%20a%20little%20before%20you%20ask%20for%20something%20from%20them%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20how%20our%20brains%20work.%20Instead%2C%20get%20them%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20ask%20three%20or%20four%20questions%20about%20their%20career.%20Genuinely%20learn%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20call%2C%20you%20could%20say%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20actually%20looking%20for%20a%20role.%20Do%20you%20happen%20to%20know%20anyone%20who%20is%20hiring%20in%20your%20company%20or%20in%20your%20network%3F%26quot%3B%20This%20way%2C%20you're%20treating%20it%20as%20a%20relationship%20rather%20than%20a%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttending%20in-person%20events%20hosted%20by%20companies%20can%20help.%20Companies%20are%20truly%20hiring%20at%20these%20events%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20orgs%20and%20agencies%20are%20hosting%20their%20own%20in-house%20mixers%20once%20a%20quarter%20that%20people%20can%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20connected%20with%20someone%20once%2C%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20that%20relationship%20warm.%20This%20could%20mean%20sending%20a%20nice%20little%20check-in%20email%20every%20three%20to%20four%20months%20to%20see%20how%20they're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245ecc735-bf0a-4b2d-8db3-1660544eac23%5C%22%3E5.%20Don't%3A%20Overdo%2C%20or%20underdo%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20mistake%20is%20refusing%20to%20post%20on%20LinkedIn%20because%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20an%20influencer.%20You're%20not%20being%20an%20influencer%20when%20you%20post%20on%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20building%20your%20personal%20brand%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20difference.%20Not%20posting%20or%20interacting%20at%20all%20won't%20help%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20mistake%20is%20taking%20it%20too%20far.%20Don't%20write%20AI-slop%20posts.%20If%20I%20see%20one%20more%20%26quot%3Bmy%20wife%20cheated%20on%20me%2C%20and%20here's%20what%20I%20learned%20about%20B2B%20sales%26quot%3B%20post%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20not%20quite%20doing%20what%20you%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20keep%20it%20simple.%20We%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20revolutionizing%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eaaad06b-0188-49a3-a1a1-23886e5addd9%5C%22%3E6.%20Do%3A%20Keep%20your%20LinkedIn%20updated%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20job%20seeker%2C%20I'd%20be%20posting%20on%20LinkedIn%20once%20a%20week.%20It%20can%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20resharing%20articles%20that%20are%20relevant%20to%20your%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwice%20a%20week%2C%20I%20would%20comment%20on%20posts%20from%20companies%20I%20want%20to%20work%20at%20or%20from%20people%20who%20work%20there.%20Besides%20having%20a%20complete%20profile%2C%20posting%20like%20that%20is%20enough%20to%20push%20you%20into%20the%20algorithm%2C%20so%20you%20become%20a%20bit%20more%20relevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20you%20need%20to%20be%20an%20influencer%20to%20get%20recognized%2C%20but%20I%20do%20think%20having%20content%20you%20can%20share%20about%20the%20value%20of%20your%20work%20online%20really%20matters.%20Whether%20that's%20LinkedIn%2C%20GitHub%20for%20engineers%2C%20or%20a%20portfolio%20for%20UX%20designers%2C%20people%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20work%20you've%20done%20and%20the%20brand%20you've%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E10%20years%20ago%2C%20I'd%20say%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20post%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20but%20today%20it's%20kind%20of%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22834b6b5e-2745-475c-9a02-35d1a3c81762%5C%22%3E7.%20Don't%3A%20Give%20companies%20an%20excuse%20to%20not%20hire%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20market%20where%20candidates%20get%20taken%20advantage%20of%2C%20employers%20should%20be%20held%20accountable.%20We%20see%20it%20in%20the%20uptick%20in%20ghosting%2C%20lowball%20offers%2C%20and%20candidates%20getting%20case%20studies%20that%20clearly%20ask%20them%20to%20work%20for%20free.%20It's%20valid%20that%20you%20want%20to%20express%20yourself%2C%20but%20doing%20it%20on%20LinkedIn%20is%20something%20to%20be%20cautious%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20recruiters%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20recruiters%20who%2C%20frankly%2C%20might%20not%20be%20great%20at%20their%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20might%20be%20scared%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20you%20because%20they're%20scared%20to%20be%20put%20on%20blast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I'd%20go%20to%20a%20website%20like%20Glassdoor%20or%20Fishbowl%2C%20since%20those%20sites%20are%20anonymous%20but%20still%20have%20the%20same%20impact.%20That%20stuff%20genuinely%20impacts%20how%20a%20company%20is%20perceived%2C%20but%20it%20protects%20you%20a%20little%20bit%20more.%20You%20can%20also%20reach%20out%20to%20that%20company's%20generic%20careers%20email%20if%20you'd%20like%20to%20give%20direct%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20careful%20on%20LinkedIn.%20The%20reality%20is%2C%20in%20an%20era%20when%20companies%20are%20finding%20every%20excuse%20not%20to%20give%20us%20a%20chance%2C%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20them%20another%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b3a5948-9764-4e64-9a59-f27487e0ad5a%5C%22%3E8.%20Do%3A%20Ask%20the%20interviewer%20about%20their%20weekend%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20skip%20small%20talk.%20Some%20people%20get%20right%20into%20business%20when%20the%20recruiter%20asks%2C%20how%20are%20you%3F%20They%20say%2C%20'good%2C'%20and%20keep%20it%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20people%20want%20to%20hire%20people%20that%20they%20want%20to%20work%20with%2C%20so%20instead%20use%20small%20talk%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20ask%20them%20a%20few%20questions.%20Such%20as%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20you%20do%20this%20weekend%3F%26quot%3B%20You're%20easier%20to%20remember%20and%20harder%20to%20ghost%20when%20you%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227e2ef9e-ead9-4959-b83a-711aed428d1b%5C%22%3E9.%20Don't%3A%20Forget%20the%20basics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20prepared%20for%20the%20basic%20questions%2C%20that's%20a%20problem.%20You%20know%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20asked%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiters-favorite-job-interview-questions-how-to-answer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETell%20me%20about%20yourself%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20you%20want%20to%20work%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20looking%20for%20a%20job%3F%26quot%3B%20Those%20are%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople's%20attention%20spans%20are%20about%20a%20minute%20and%20a%20half%20per%20answer.%20If%20you're%20giving%20two-%2C%20three-%2C%20or%20four-minute%20interview%20answers%2C%20you've%20already%20lost%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20lots%20of%20filler%20words%2C%20or%20pretending%20that%20you%20have%20the%20answers%20when%20you%20don't%2C%20is%20a%20mistake.%20Keep%20it%20short%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22816c95ee-b947-4c74-a5c8-4c47d6ef9370%5C%22%3E10.%20Do%3A%20Be%20freeflowing%2C%20no%20scripts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20ones%20I%20see%20more%20and%20more%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%20is%20people%20reading%20off%20scripts%2C%20especially%20in%20virtual%20interviews%2C%20where%20you've%20got%20your%20notes%2C%20and%20it's%20clear%20you're%20reading.%20Interviews%20are%20conversations%2C%20not%20interrogations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20want%20to%20show%20that%20you%20have%20the%20skills%20and%20cultural%20alignment%2C%20and%20you%20can%20only%20do%20that%20by%20being%20a%20person%20%E2%80%94%20well-prepared%20but%20free-flowing%2C%20not%20scripted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bae9f560-d365-4e7c-a79c-56e32c30ae5c%5C%22%3E11.%20Don't%3A%20Overly%20use%20the%20word%20'we'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAvoid%20overly%20using%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bwe%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BI.%26quot%3B%20When%20you're%20asked%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20work%2C%20and%20you%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20this%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bour%20team%20did%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20can%20sound%20great%20because%20you're%20being%20inclusive%2C%20but%20recruiters%20want%20to%20hear%20what%20you%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Edid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20hiring%20you%2C%20not%20the%20whole%20team.%20If%20everything%20is%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20%26quot%3Bwe%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20may%20assume%20you%20didn't%20have%20a%20big%20role.%20You%20need%20balance%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%2030%25%20%26quot%3Bwe%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20rest%20should%20be%20specific%20about%20your%20individual%20contributions.%20If%20you%20can't%20say%20that%20clearly%2C%20the%20recruiter%20will%20assume%20it%20wasn't%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5a0371b-bdc0-41e9-824c-83bf76ea77bd%5C%22%3E12.%20Do%3A%20Turn%20off%20social%20media%20when%20needed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20fall%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-doomscrolling-tracking-film-podcasts-books-analog-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edoomscrolling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20talk%20about%20social%20media%20doomscrolling%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20LinkedIn%20doomscrolling%20is%20real%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20in%20the%20job%20search%2C%20it's%20OK%20to%20not%20open%20LinkedIn%20beyond%20what%20you%20need%20to%20build%20your%20brand.%20A%20lot%20of%20what%20you're%20seeing%20is%20intense%20highlight%20reels%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20actually%20know%20how%20people%20are%20performing%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20urge%20people%20to%20disconnect%20during%20their%20job%20search%20process.%20It's%20also%20OK%20to%20mute%20keywords%20like%20%26quot%3Bjob%20hunting%26quot%3B%20on%20TikTok%2C%20because%20seeing%20someone%20on%20day%201%2C000%20of%20job%20hunting%20can%20add%20to%20anxiety%20unnecessarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222bf81955-e434-436a-850d-7f27fa57fd5e%5C%22%3EIf%20today%20were%20day%20one%20of%20my%20job%20search%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20structure%20my%20job%20search%20in%20shifts.%20For%20example%2C%20Mondays%20are%20for%20applying%2C%20Tuesdays%20are%20for%20reaching%20out%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20Wednesdays%20are%20for%20attending%20networking%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreating%20it%20like%20shift%20work%20helps%20prevent%20burnout%2C%20because%20even%20if%20you%20do%20everything%20right%2C%20it%20can%20still%20take%20time.%20You%20have%20to%20preserve%20your%20sanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-recruiter-shares-advice-resumes-networking-strategies-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782119102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a344a5af4bed3c6152cbd9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-recruiter-shares-advice-resumes-networking-strategies-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20recruiter%20turned%20content%20creator%20offers%20insights%20on%20job%20market%20navigation%2C%20including%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20crafting%2C%20networking%2C%20and%20LinkedIn%20engagement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alyshia%20Hull)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20explorers%20really%20find%20Egyptian-style%20artefacts%20in%20the%20Grand%20Canyon%3F%20Why%20experts%20remain%20sceptical%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782119089000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131905026%2Cimgsize-1307489.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fdid-explorers-really-find-egyptian-style-artefacts-in-the-grand-canyon-why-experts-remain-sceptical%2Farticleshow%2F131904967.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131904967.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fdid-explorers-really-find-egyptian-style-artefacts-in-the-grand-canyon-why-experts-remain-sceptical%2Farticleshow%2F131904967.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fdid-explorers-really-find-egyptian-style-artefacts-in-the-grand-canyon-why-experts-remain-sceptical%2Famp_articleshow%2F131904967.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fdid-explorers-really-find-egyptian-style-artefacts-in-the-grand-canyon-why-experts-remain-sceptical%2Famp_articleshow%2F131904967.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Venice%20Film%20Festival%20Jury%3A%20Johnnie%20To%2C%20Kaouther%20Ben%20Hania%2C%20Shahrbanoo%20Sadat%20and%20More%20Join%20President%20Maggie%20Gyllenhaal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782119025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236786943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20main%20jury%20roster%20for%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%C2%A0Venice%20Film%20Festival%C2%A0has%20been%20unveiled%2C%20with%20Hong%20Kong%20filmmaking%20giant%20Johnnie%20To%2C%20Tunisian%20director%20Kaouther%20Ben%20Hania%20and%20Afghan%20filmmaker%20Shahrbanoo%20Sadat%20among%20those%20joining%20previously%20announced%20competition%20president%20Maggie%20Gyllenhaal.%20To%20will%20be%20returning%20as%20a%20Venice%20juror%20after%20previously%20being%20on%20the%20same%20jury%20in%202008.%20Four%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Nvivarelli%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sam%20Altman's%20Orb%20startup%20investigated%20financial%20misconduct%20allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20and%20Orb%2C%20a%20volleyball-sized%20biometric%20device%20developed%20by%20Tools%20for%20Humanity.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3417a80e60dfb3f373f13e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKylie%20Cooper%2FReuters%3B%20Christina%20House%2FLos%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETools%20for%20Humanity%2C%20Sam%20Altman's%20eyeball-scanning%20startup%2C%20hired%20two%20law%20firms%20last%20year%20to%20investigate%20allegations%20of%20financial%20irregularities%20at%20the%20company%20and%20bribery%20of%20foreign%20officials%20in%20Thailand%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20investigations%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20probes%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned%2C%20looked%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einto%20Tools%20for%20Humanity's%20rollout%20in%20Thailand%20with%20a%20company%20linked%20to%20a%20South%20African%20businessman%20whom%20U.S.%20and%20Thai%20officials%20have%20accused%20of%20involvement%20in%20transnational%20cyber-fraud%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20investigation%20reviewed%20concerns%20including%20allegations%20that%20senior%20company%20leaders%20approved%20six-%20and%20seven-figure%20payments%20to%20a%20foreign%20firm%20to%20boost%20the%20value%20of%20the%20Worldcoin%20token%2C%20a%20potential%20violation%20of%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20rules%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20investigations%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20investigations%2C%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20severed%20ties%20with%20a%20business%20partner%20in%20Thailand%20and%20strengthened%20its%20policies%20and%20controls%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Following%20the%20investigations%2C%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20said%20it%20is%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20facts%20establishing%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act%2C%20a%20federal%20anti-bribery%20law%2C%20by%20the%20company%20or%20any%20of%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225473%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20has%20his%20iris%20scanned%20with%20an%20orb%2C%20a%20biometric%20data%20scanning%20device%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20Worldcoin%20cryptocurrency%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%20on%20March%2022%2C%202024.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a34221ff4bed3c6152cbaad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223649%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETools%20for%20Humanity's%20Orb%20scans%20irises%20to%20create%20a%20digital%20ID%20that%20proves%20a%20user%20is%20human.%3Cp%3EJuan%20Mabromata%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20concerns%20are%20raised%2C%20we%20take%20them%20seriously%2C%20engage%20independent%20outside%20experts%20to%20review%20them%20when%20appropriate%2C%20and%20take%20action%20as%20warranted%20based%20on%20what%20we%20learn%2C%20as%20we%20are%20doing%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETools%20for%20Humanity%20was%20cofounded%20by%20one%20of%20the%20tech%20world's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-chatgpt-worldcoin-helion-future-tech-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20notable%20figures%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Altman%2C%20better%20known%20for%20his%20role%20as%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20is%20one%20of%20three%20people%20on%20Tools%20for%20Humanity's%20board.%20Valued%20in%202023%20at%20%242.5%20billion%2C%20it%20has%20raised%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20from%20investors%20such%20as%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20Bain%20Capital%2C%20and%20Khosla%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20goal%3A%20to%20distinguish%20humans%20from%20AI%20bots%20with%20iris%20scans%20performed%20by%20a%20volleyball-sized%20sphere%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BOrb.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20didn't%20respond%20to%20emailed%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e84b6d94-932b-4db0-98a7-c6138fd84e35%5C%22%3EA%20staffer%20raises%20concerns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20of%20the%20reviews%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20engaged%20law%20firm%20O'Melveny%20%26amp%3B%20Myers.%20The%20purpose%20of%20that%20investigation%20was%20to%20look%20into%20concerns%20raised%20by%20a%20company%20staffer%20about%20potential%20misuse%20of%20company%20funds%2C%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20investigations%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Melveny%20examined%20allegations%20of%20personal%20expenses%20and%20corporate%20housing%20charged%20on%20company%20credit%20cards%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20The%20firm%20also%20looked%20into%20alleged%20misclassification%20of%20full-time%20employees%20as%20contractors%20to%20lower%20the%20employees'%20tax%20burden%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20auditing%20firm%2C%20BDO%2C%20also%20looked%20into%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20company%20staffer%20about%20the%20startup's%20financials%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20BDO%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224344%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Worldcoin%20Project%20Co-founders%20Alex%20Blania%20(L)%20and%20Sam%20Altman%20(R).%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3420e9c7a58f814f0d4134%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222896%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETools%20for%20Humanity%20was%20co-founded%20by%20Alex%20Blania%20(left)%20and%20Sam%20Altman.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20said%20it%20hired%20the%20law%20firm%20Sidley%20Austin.%20That%20firm%20looked%20into%20whether%20the%20company's%20dealings%20in%20Thailand%20had%20violated%20the%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act%2C%20these%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act%20is%20a%20federal%20law%20that%20prohibits%20companies%20from%20paying%2C%20offering%2C%20or%20promising%20bribes%20to%20foreign%20officials%20to%20obtain%20or%20retain%20business.%20Civil%20and%20criminal%20penalties%20can%20include%20hefty%20fines%20and%20prison%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFindings%20from%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20law%20firm%20investigations%20were%20presented%20to%20the%20company's%20board%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20investigations.%20Tools%20for%20Humanity's%20directors%20are%20Altman%2C%20Chief%20Executive%20Alex%20Blania%2C%20and%20Spencer%20Bogart%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Blockchain%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20conducting%20business%20ethically%20around%20the%20world%20and%20adhering%20to%20the%20law%20wherever%20we%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20maintain%20robust%20policies%20and%20practices%20designed%20to%20support%20that%20commitment%2C%20we%20enforce%20them%2C%20and%20we%20strengthen%20them%20when%20we%20identify%20areas%20for%20improvement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2a9b055-555b-420e-b209-c6bfd14f45dc%5C%22%3ERegulatory%20roadblocks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETools%20for%20Humanity%20was%20cofounded%20in%202019%20by%20Altman%20and%20Blania%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-chatgpt-worldcoin-helion-future-tech-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethen%20a%20young%20physics%20researcher%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Caltech.%20The%20company%20builds%20tools%20for%20the%20Cayman%20Islands-based%20World%20Foundation%2C%20which%20distributes%20the%20Worldcoin%20cryptocurrency%20token%20and%20aims%20to%20develop%20a%20global%20identity%20and%20financial%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20offered%20new%20participants%20the%20option%20to%20claim%20tokens%20of%20Worldcoin.%20Some%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20staffers%20have%20received%20token%20grants%20as%20part%20of%20their%20compensation%20packages.%20Early%20investors%20in%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20also%20received%20tokens%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhitepaper.world.org%2Fdesigning-for-scale%23wld-token-allocation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hand%20holding%20smartphone%20running%20World%20app%20displaying%20unlocked%20Worldcoin%20balance%20of%2039.22%2C%20Union%20Square%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California%2C%20May%2020%2C%202025.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3423000e60dfb3f373f24c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20participants%20were%20given%20the%20option%20to%20claim%20Worldcoin%20tokens%20after%20their%20iris%20scan.%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGado%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20the%20Worldcoin%20token%20stood%20at%20around%2061%20cents%20Sunday%2C%20a%20decline%20of%2095%25%20since%20its%20peak%20of%20%2411.79%20in%20March%202024%2C%20according%20to%20Coinbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20company%20tries%20to%20recruit%20users%20for%20its%20World%20app%20and%20network%2C%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-orb-eye-scanning-startup-billion-user-goal-viability-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emet%20regulatory%20roadblocks%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20questions%20about%20its%20iris-scanning%20and%20data%20collection.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20barred%2C%20paused%2C%20or%20investigated%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20including%20Spain%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20the%20company%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-tools-for-humanity-startup-culture-hardcore-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall-or-nothing%20work%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20A%20slew%20of%20high-level%20staffers%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-level-departures-tools-for-humanity-sam-altman-alex-blania-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20%3C%2Fa%3Eover%20the%20past%20year%2C%20and%20in%20June%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-orb-worldcoin-tools-for-humanity-layoffs-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20layoffs%20affected%20less%20than%2015%25%20of%20the%20company's%20global%20workforce%20of%20roughly%20500%20people%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20recently%20entered%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20its%20plan%2C%20focusing%20on%20building%20partnerships%20with%20businesses%20and%20demonstrating%20utility%20to%20users%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworld.org%2Fblog%2Ffoundational-topics%2Fthesimpleplan%23phase-3-reach-critical-scale-and-initial-utility%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b35e2347-1433-4871-9c8e-33a23a84b56f%5C%22%3EA%20questionable%20business%20partner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETools%20for%20Humanity%20has%20drawn%20scrutiny%20for%20its%20operations%20in%20Asia.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technologyreview.com%2F2022%2F04%2F06%2F1048981%2Fworldcoin-cryptocurrency-biometrics-web3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20MIT%20Technology%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20launched%20an%20investigation%20after%20the%20magazine's%20reporting%20showed%20that%20the%20company's%20contractor%20in%20Indonesia%20had%20made%20payments%20to%20village%20officials%2C%20a%20potential%20violation%20of%20the%20country's%20anti-corruption%20and%20anti-bribery%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225404%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20abandoned%20building%20bearing%20the%20Worldcoin%20logo%20is%20seen%20at%20an%20upscale%20residential%20area%20in%20Jakarta%20on%20May%205%2C%202025.%20Indonesian%20authorities%20said%20they%20have%20suspended%20Worldcoin%2C%20the%20eyeball-scanning%20cryptocurrency%20project%20co-founded%20by%20OpenAI%20chief%20Sam%20Altman%20under%20scrutiny%20in%20several%20countries.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3421b2f4bed3c6152cbaa7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223603%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETools%20for%20Humanity's%20operations%20were%20suspended%20in%20Indonesia.%3Cp%3EBay%20Ismoyo%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20September%2C%20Whale%20Hunting%2C%20an%20investigative%20journalism%20project%20run%20by%20the%20production%20company%20Brazen%2C%20reported%20that%20during%20Tools%20for%20Humanity's%20rollout%20in%20Thailand%2C%20the%20startup%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhalehunting.projectbrazen.com%2Fsam-altmans-worldcoin-partnered-with-1-5-billion-criminal-network-in-thailand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunwittingly%20done%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company%20tied%20to%20South%20African%20businessman%20Benjamin%20Mauerberger%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Ben%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThai%20courts%20have%20seized%20assets%20belonging%20to%20Mauerberger%20and%20issued%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20him%20on%20fraud%20and%20money%20laundering%20charges%20related%20to%20an%20alleged%20transnational%20scam%20network%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Fsoutheast-asia%2Farticle%2F3349581%2Fthailand-snatches-us260-million-cross-border-scammers-decisive-crackdown%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enews%20outlets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bill%20advanced%20in%20December%20by%20the%20House%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Committee%20named%20Mauerberger%20on%20a%20list%20of%20foreign%20nationals%20who%20could%20be%20subject%20to%20sanctions%20for%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20transnational%20%26quot%3Bpig%20butchering%26quot%3B%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETools%20for%20Humanity%20%26quot%3Bentered%20into%20business%20with%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20region%20linked%20to%20an%20individual%20about%20whom%20serious%20allegations%20later%20emerged%2C%20but%20who%20had%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20false%20name%20and%20about%20whom%20those%20allegations%20were%20not%20known%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20company%20learned%20of%20the%20allegations%2C%20it%20retained%20Sidley%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%2C%20severed%20ties%2C%20and%20implemented%20more%20robust%20due%20diligence%20measures%20for%20vetting%20business%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Blania%20speaks%20onstage%20during%20Sam%20Altman's%20World%20Celebration%20for%20the%20US%20Launch%20at%20Fort%20Mason%20Center%20on%20April%2030%2C%202025%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3423fbc7a58f814f0d416b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222339%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETools%20for%20Humanity's%20iris-scanning%20Orbs%20came%20to%20the%20US%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EKimberly%