Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20employees%20face%20high-stakes%20financial%20decisions%20with%20IPOs%20coming%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20companies'%20rapid%20growth%20has%20boosted%20workers'%20equity%20at%20staggering%20rates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20employees'%20financial%20advisors%20to%20see%20what%20advice%20they're%20giving%20pre-IPO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-anthropic-ai-ipo-spacex-stocks-stock-market-investing-trade-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20hit%20the%20public%20markets%2C%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20employees%20are%20going%20to%20become%20gobsmackingly%20rich.%20That%20means%20it's%20time%20for%20some%20high-stakes%20financial%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20AI%20labs%20recently%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fan-ipo-before-openai-that-could-be-a-trap-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20initial%20paperwork%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20go%20public%2C%20preparing%20to%20turn%20their%20nearly%20%241%20trillion%20in%C2%A0private%20valuations%20into%20stock-market%20windfalls.%20For%20employees%2C%20life-changing%20money%20is%20on%20its%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20behind%20Claude%20and%20ChatGPT%20have%20major%20decisions%20to%20make.%20When%20should%20they%20sell%20their%20shares%3F%20Is%20it%20a%20good%20time%20to%20shell%20out%20for%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20house%20in%20San%20Francisco%3F%20What's%20the%20right%20way%20to%20donate%20to%20charity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20these%20workers%20aren't%20getting%20advice%20from%20their%20chatbots%2C%20they%20turn%20to%20accountants%20and%20money%20managers.%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20several%20financial%20planners%20who%20are%20already%20working%20with%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20employees%20to%20learn%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-employees-sell-stock-avoid-capital-gains-tax-spacex-ipos-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etax%20and%20planning%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20advisors%20are%20giving%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224dbcf969-bcfb-4fe2-a0a0-94d7a5b80df2%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20workers%20need%20to%20know%20what%20they've%20got%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20financial%20planner%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20offered%20the%20same%20advice%3A%20know%20what%20you've%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Mark%20Cecchini%2C%20a%20wealth%20planning%20advisor%2C%20said%20that%20one%20of%20his%20clients%20at%20Anthropic%20has%20worked%20at%20the%20company%20for%20only%20three%20years%20and%20already%20has%20a%20whopping%20%2440%20million%20in%20vested%20equity%2C%20with%20another%20%2430%20million%20still%20to%20vest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20workers%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20sell%20their%20shares%20on%20IPO%20day%20to%20use%20all%20that%20money%20immediately.%20Companies%20and%20banks%20typically%20impose%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-spcx-stock-lockup-period-expire-nasdaq-elon-musk-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elock-up%20period%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20employees%2C%20delaying%20when%20they%20can%20cash%20out.%20SpaceX%20revealed%20its%20lock-up%20structure%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20before%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-former-employee-wealth-managers-swag-ipo-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einitial%20public%20offering%20this%20June%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20should%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20that%20timeline%C2%A0and%20closely%20track%20the%C2%A0tax%20bills%20and%20credits%20they've%20already%20incurred%20from%20their%20stock%20options%2C%20financial%20planner%20Bryan%20Hasling%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20As%20an%20advisor%2C%20he%20tries%20to%20stop%20clients%20from%20spending%20money%20they%20don't%20yet%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Anthropic%20goes%20public%20in%20October%2C%20it%20could%20be%20April%20before%20employees%20can%20cash%20out%20their%20shares%2C%20Hasling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20really%20important%20because%20people%20hear%20'IPO'%20and%20their%20brain%20starts%20going%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20Hasling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259a9dba3-881a-46b5-bd82-54ebcdf5d2fe%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20staff%20should%20decide%20in%20advance%20how%20much%20to%20cash%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHasling%20has%20another%20go-to%20piece%20of%20advice%3A%20%26quot%3BJust%20know%20your%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20make%20two%20common%20mistakes%20during%20and%20after%20IPOs%2C%20Hasling%20said%3A%20they%20view%20their%20share%20value%20as%20liquid%20cash%20%E2%80%94%20ignoring%20the%20future%20tax%20hit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20go%20in%20without%20an%20established%20goal%20for%20their%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20should%20think%20about%20what%20they'd%20like%20to%20do%20with%20life-changing%20wealth%2C%20Hasling%20said%2C%20be%20it%20to%20retire%2C%20start%20angel%20investing%2C%20pay%20off%20their%20parents'%20mortgages%2C%20or%2C%20as%20is%20most%20often%20the%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-cant-afford-home-san-francisco-i-make-a-lot-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuy%20a%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20plan%20for%20those%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20advisor%20said%20workers%20get%20sucked%20into%20the%20visceral%20feeling%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-ai-investing-strategy-wall-street-investing-spacex-spcx-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewatching%20their%20stock%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20net%20worth%20go%20up%20and%20down%2C%20when%20they'd%20have%20been%20better%20off%20setting%20a%20firm%20cash-out%20plan%20before%20the%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20know%20that%20big%20round%20number%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20capture%20it%2C%20pay%20tax%2C%20improve%20your%20sleep%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20Hasling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Cecchini's%20clients%2C%20an%20OpenAI%20employee%2C%20is%20eyeing%20a%20%246%20million%20house%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area's%20swanky%20Marin%20County.%20The%20advisor%20said%20he's%20helping%20the%20client%20consider%20loans%2C%20potentially%20against%20pre-IPO%20shares%2C%20to%20get%20the%20deal%20done.%20If%20employees%20can't%20cash%20out%20until%20spring%2C%20Cecchini%20said%2C%20that'll%20be%20a%20brutal%20time%20to%20buy%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-housing-market-real-estate-home-prices-ai-boom-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBay%20Area%20housing%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20in%20bidding%20wars%20with%20people%20that%20have%20potentially%20unlimited%20liquidity%20if%20everything%20goes%20their%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Cecchini%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20planners%20largely%20avoid%20advising%20clients%20on%20whether%20to%20hold%20or%20sell%20their%20company's%20stock%2C%20though%20they%20generally%20support%20diversification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinnie%20Lau%2C%20an%20accountant%20with%20clients%20at%20both%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20poses%20a%20thought%20experiment%20to%20tech%20workers.%20Would%20they%20rather%20take%20a%20bag%20with%20a%20%24100%2C000%20cash%20bonus%20or%20%24100%2C000%20in%20company%20stock%20options%3F%20They're%20each%20taxed%20as%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20client%20says%20they'd%20like%20the%20cash%2C%20Lau%20encourages%20them%20to%20view%20the%20company%20going%20public%20as%20a%20good%20time%20to%20sell.%20If%20they'd%20like%20the%20stock%2C%20she%20asks%20how%20much%20they'd%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20per%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%2C%20do%20you%20think%20your%20company's%20stock%20is%20going%20to%20beat%20every%20single%20thing%20out%20there%3F%26quot%3B%20Lau%20said.%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20comfortable%20not%20diversifying%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22458f7f2e-4c54-41fe-bee9-7da38e7516a1%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20employees%20will%20need%20to%20manage%20the%20tax%20bill%20of%20a%20lifetime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%2C%20where%20the%20AI%20labs%20are%20based%2C%20has%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fstate-income-tax-rates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enation's%20highest%20state%20tax%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20federal%20taxes%20jump%20up%20when%20a%20worker%20has%20an%20incredibly%20lucrative%20year.%20Cecchini%20said%20he%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20%26quot%3Bjust%20prepping%20people%20for%20that%20sticker%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20have%20given%20different%20types%20of%20stock%20options%20to%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20a%20rare%20breed.%20Because%20of%20the%20company's%20former%20nonprofit%20status%2C%20early%20employees%20received%20equity%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Profit%20Participation%20Units%2C%20a%20customized%20payment%20that's%20tied%20to%20future%20profits.%20More%20recently%2C%20OpenAI%20has%20handed%20out%20the%20more%20traditional%20Restricted%20Stock%20Units%2C%20and%20PPUs%20have%20begun%20converting%20to%20regular%20shares%2C%20making%20tax%20planning%20simpler%2C%20Cecchini%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-rewriting-startup-pay-levels-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20paid%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20more%20classic%20mix%20of%20stock-based%20compensation%2C%20distributing%20RSUs%2C%20Non-Qualified%20Stock%20Options%2C%20and%20Incentive%20Stock%20Options.%20Those%20are%20a%20bit%20trickier%20to%20plan%20around%2C%20tax-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvisors%20suggested%20some%20workarounds%20and%20strategies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fwhat-is-tax-liability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20reduce%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fwhat-is-tax-liability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20tax%20liability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20workers%20exercise%20ISOs%2C%20they%20may%20end%20up%20paying%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhats-the-alternative-minimum-tax-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlternative%20Minimum%20Tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20their%20regular%20tax%20bill%2C%20and%20it's%20possible%20to%20use%20that%20payment%20as%20a%20credit%20against%20future%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECecchini%20saw%20an%20OpenAI%20client%20use%20the%20opportunity%20zone%20deferral%2C%20which%20incentivizes%20investment%20in%20certain%20areas%20by%20deferring%20capital%20gain%20taxes.%20He's%20also%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BBuy%2C%20borrow%2C%20die%26quot%3B%20strategy%20of%20borrowing%20against%20brokerage%20accounts%20to%20avoid%20paying%20capital%20gains%20taxes%2C%20which%20he%20said%20works%20best%20if%20you%20feel%20super%20confident%20in%20your%20portfolio's%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20who%20may%20have%20been%20through%20a%20failed%20IPO%20or%20held%20bad%20investments%20can%20use%20those%20prior%20losses%20to%20reduce%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20on%20their%20OpenAI%20or%20Anthropic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-protest-elon-musk-wall-street-investing-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIPO%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Evan%20Hargreaves%2C%20an%20accountant%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHargreaves%2C%20who%20has%20clients%20at%20both%20labs%2C%20said%20he's%20recently%20seen%20more%20everyday%20people%20put%20their%20stocks%20into%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonor-advised-fund-big-beautiful-bill-philanthropy-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edonor-advised%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20accounts%20that%20give%20to%20charities%2C%C2%A0to%20reduce%20their%20tax%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20good%20route%20for%20these%20workers%2C%20he%20said.%20If%20they%20donate%20the%20shares%20that%20have%20gained%20the%20most%20value%20over%20time%20to%20the%20funds%2C%20they%20both%20get%20a%20deduction%20for%20the%20donation%20and%20avoid%20paying%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20on%20the%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHargreaves%20also%20suggests%20the%20easiest%20route%20to%20clients%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-age-just-started-retirement-planning-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaxing%20out%20your%20401(k)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20year%20of%20an%20IPO%20can%20save%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20advisors%20say%20to%20be%20prepared%2C%20as%20many%20IPOs%20underperform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20doomer%20and%20say%2C%20'Oh%2C%20bad%20things%20happen%2C'%20but%20educated%20people%20know%20what%20the%20stats%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Hargreaves%20said.%20%26quot%3BEh%2C%20that%20sounds%20so%20negative.%20You%20just%20want%20to%20be%20prepared%20whether%20the%20stock%20goes%20up%20or%20down%20on%20IPO%2C%20six%20months%20to%20a%20year%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ascouncil%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Escouncil%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20over%20text%2C%20Signal%2C%20Telegram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp%20at%20415-757-8198.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20here's%20our%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin