a.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20losing%20both%20parents%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20Rupam%20Sonali%20vowed%20to%20fulfill%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20dream.%20At%2022%2C%20she%20cleared%20the%20Jharkhand%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20exam%20on%20her%20very%20first%20attempt%20without%20any%20formal%20coaching%20support.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496969%2Frupam-sonali-jpsc-jharkhand-public-service-commission-success-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Inspired%20by%20Avatar%E2%80%99s%20Pandora%E2%80%99%3A%20Meet%20the%20Naturalist%20Duo%20Behind%20India%E2%80%99s%201st%20Private%20Biosphere%20in%20Uttarakhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20August%2020234.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20usually%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%3F%20Is%20it%20the%20doorbell%2C%20an%20alarm%2C%20or%20perhaps%20a%20family%20member%3F%20Now%2C%20imagine%20waking%20up%20to%20the%20calls%20of%20a%20leopard%20or%20a%20sambar%20deer%20instead!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20Dhar%20Gupta%20experiences%20this%20every%20day%20at%20his%20biosphere%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20nestled%20in%20the%20Shivalik%20foothills%2C%20overlooking%20the%20stunning%20Raghati%20river.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajaji%20Raghati%20biosphere%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20sit%20on%20a%20rock%20and%20watch%20as%20leopards%2C%20